  "title": "Receptionist (Part Time / Full Time / Training provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet and engage clients with warmth, style, and professionalism</li>\n  <li>Assist with appointment bookings and daily operations</li>\n  <li>Support our beauty team in delivering a seamless client experience</li>\n  <li>Ensure our space looks and feels welcoming at all times</li>\n  <li>Be the go-to person for information, service, and care</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Vibrant, energetic, and passionate about beauty &amp; wellness</li>\n  <li>Friendly, approachable, and confident communicator</li>\n  <li>Loves being around people and thrives in a social environment</li>\n  <li>Well-groomed with a natural sense of style</li>\n  <li>No experience needed – training provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What’s In It For You</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Full-time role (5–6 days work week, negotiable). For part-time roles, apply to discuss.</li>\n  <li>Attractive career pathway within the beauty industry</li>\n  <li>Vibrant, youthful, and supportive work culture</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to grow into sales, beauty, training, supervisory or managerial roles</li>\n  <li>Be part of an exciting industry where you can shine every day</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
